# pmi-ingest configuration moved to the platform-root single source of truth:
#   /Users/reid/micah/pmi_data_platform/.env
#
# This file is kept only as a pointer; pmi-ingest's pydantic-settings probes
# all three of: cwd `.env`, this service-root `.env` (legacy), and the
# platform-root `pmi_data_platform/.env` (current).
#
# pmi-ingest specifically reads:
#   - POLYMARKET_BASE_URL / POLYMARKET_POLL_INTERVAL_SEC
#   - POLYMARKET_PAGE_SIZE / POLYMARKET_MAX_PAGES
#   - POLYMARKET_USE_MOCK / POLYMARKET_MOCK_FIXTURE_PATH   ← A: bypass live HTTP
# Plus everything pmi-core needs (PMI_DB_*, PMI_LOG_LEVEL).
#
# Bootstrap a fresh checkout:
#   cp pmi_data_platform/.env.example pmi_data_platform/.env
